The Peter Schiff Show
Monday, 20 February 2012


[sebaygo1]


The Schiff Radio web site describes today\'s broadcast as: Two hours of The Peter Schiff Show, the golden standard in talk radio.

This is a \"best of\" collection of clips from previous broadcasts. It begins with Peter\'s conversation with Sen. Jim DeMint, from January 26.
